dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Ralph Phillips. May I have your name, please?
Hello, Ralph. My name is Patricia Evans.
Nice to meet you, Patricia. Can you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, it's seven eight six nine five.
Thank you, Patricia. Could you also confirm your date of birth for security purposes?
Of course, it's the ninth of August, nineteen sixty-seven.
Thank you for the information, Patricia. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
I was wondering about adding a new vehicle to my policy.
I can definitely help you with that. Can you provide me with the make and model of the vehicle?
Thank you for your time, Patricia. If you have any further questions, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
